  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare in patients with critical limb ischemia the efficacy of
      angioplasty with different paclitaxel-eluting balloon devices for below-the-knee lesions in
      terms of restenosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Two devices will be evaluated: the Lutonix and the Freeway paclitaxel eluting balloons. A
      post-hoc analysis will compare the results with the historical data from DEBATE-BTK
      (NCT01558505).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
